Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Airline cartel claim
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043www7
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Nov 1982
Transatlantic price-fixing between major airlines put Laker out of business claims law suit. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less